Key design decisions:
- 16 named ANSI colors use Claude Dark theme-appropriate warm tones
- xterm-256 uses standard 6x6x6 RGB cube (indices 16-231) + 24 grayscale (232-255)
- Named Foreground/Background variants map to theme defaults
- Grid extraction iterates row-major, producing GridCell with converted fg/bg colors
